<TITLE> Mother, son killed as truck ploughs into rickshaw </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Mar 21 (bdnews24.com)A mother and son were killed when a truck slammed into a rickshaw in Maizbagh, Ishwarganj, at around 7.30am Saturday, said police. Thirty-five year-old Rahima and seven year-old Nasiruddin were killed outright, Mymensingh additional police super ASM Akhteruzzaman told bdnews24. The rickshaw driver was injured. The truck driver managed to flee the scene. bdn
